    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This specification describes an RTP payload format for the VP9 video codec.  The payload format has wide applicability as it supports applications from low bitrate peer-to-peer usage to high bitrate video conferences.  It includes provisions for temporal and spatial scalability.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
